  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Cook gluten-free pasta according to package instructions.",
    "In a large pan, saute onion and garlic until softened.",
    "Add bhuna spice mix and cook for 1 minute.",
    "In a large bowl, combine cooked pasta, chwinamul, and sauteed onion mixture.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix heavy cream and shredded mozzarella cheese.",
    "Add the cream mixture to the pasta mixture and stir until combined.",
    "Place norwegian salmon fillet on top of the pasta mixture.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and bake for 25 minutes."
